      "description": "Simulated hydraulic head-flow curves compared against in-vitro measurements for three impeller speeds (2000, 2750, 3500 rpm). Predicted pressure rise agrees within 3.1% RMS across the operating envelope. Turbulence model (SST k-omega) selected based on prior sensitivity study showing lowest systematic bias for confined rotating flows.",
