      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution comparison against PIV measurements",
      "description": "Volume-averaged scalar shear stress and peak shear stress locus compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) data from literature. Spatial correlation coefficient R = 0.91. Peak shear stress location correctly predicted in volute cutwater region for all tested speeds.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
