      "rationale": "Validation QoIs (NIH, hydraulic head, peak shear stress) are the direct computational precursors to the COU decision metric (RH index). Transformation from NIH to RH is analytic and well-established (ASTM F1841). Relevance of QoIs is confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
