      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the reference geometry for the COU device family. Operating conditions overlap COU envelope. Geometric differences between validation and COU device (minor volute modification) assessed via sensitivity study; impact on NIH < 2%. Validation activities are sufficiently relevant to the COU."
